{"tid":438092,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】賰輸身家揾莊家尋仇真係好咩? Day136  16/10","createTime":"2017-10-16T14:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T17:36:13.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0daa8740ac413836c355f3ad7c6e8b3c94b7a851","tid":438092,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:49:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點半左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=%2FUX9rVaHPl4ydFy5%2FHb2rdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=4e1075a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=%2FUX9rVaHPl4ydFy5%2FHb2rdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f58b1f52\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=%2FUX9rVaHPl4ydFy5%2FHb2rdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=480cba1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">請各位多多支持，比D錢黎洗下</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"8ad30d6607898e07084058fad077db744b9b87bb","tid":438092,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:33:23.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97989dae8faa7f50392efb55e84ee2420ec47948","tid":438092,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1187808c82f34c04318f98819fbbec87c04adc","tid":438092,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b49871c2d84d0f5dcec328eb4e1095d217c7be","tid":438092,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20127db96345bbce78526562565d22aca18e0d02","tid":438092,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3749d35621b1e6e33ebd7d37c90cf29b5eeb019","tid":438092,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddcb977d2673b4cc71a19bb43725dcb8e0f0286","tid":438092,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65e5dc6f30e78f1d345ecf9241e2533bd421f63","tid":438092,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gi